BTTTriggers.BTTPredefinedActionName: Run Apple Script (enter directly as text)
BTTTriggers.BTTInlineAppleScript: if application "Safari" is running then	tell application "Safari"		repeat with w in windows			repeat with t in tabs of w				tell t					if URL starts with "http://www.youtube.com/watch" or URL starts with "https://www.youtube.com/watch" then						set index of w to 1						delay 0.1						set current tab of w to t					end if				end tell			end repeat		end repeat	end tellend if

BTTTriggerConfig.BTTTouchBarAppleScriptString: if application "Safari" is running then	tell application "Safari"		repeat with t in tabs of windows			tell t				if URL starts with "http://www.youtube.com/watch" or URL starts with "https://www.youtube.com/watch" then					return text 1 thru -11 of (name of t as text)				end if			end tell		end repeat	end tellend ifreturn ""

BTTTriggers.BTTPredefinedActionName: Run Apple Script (enter directly as text)
BTTTriggers.BTTInlineAppleScript: if application "Safari" is running then	tell application "Safari"		repeat with w in windows			repeat with t in tabs of w				tell t					if URL starts with "https://music.yandex.ru" and name does not end with " ." then --  ,   						set index of w to 1						delay 0.1						set current tab of w to t					end if				end tell			end repeat		end repeat	end tellend if

BTTTriggerConfig.BTTTouchBarAppleScriptString: if application "Safari" is running then	tell application "Safari"		repeat with t in tabs of windows			tell t				if URL starts with "https://music.yandex.ru" and name does not end with " ." then					return name of t as text				end if			end tell		end repeat	end tellend ifreturn ""

BTTTriggers.BTTPredefinedActionName: Open URL / Open URL With Selection

BTTTriggerConfig.BTTTouchBarAppleScriptString:
# This script requires two libs. Download them:# https://itunes.apple.com/ru/app/json-helper-for-applescript/id453114608?l=en&mt=12 # https://itunes.apple.com/ru/app/location-helper-for-applescript/id488536386?mt=12 tell application "JSON Helper"	set weather to fetch JSON from "http://api.openweathermap.org/data/2.5/weather?lat=55.018803&lon=82.933952&units=metric&appid=32c4256d09a4c52b38aecddba7a078f6"	set temp to temp of main of weather as string	set wind to speed of wind of weather as string	return temp & "C
" & wind & "m/s"end tell

BTTTriggers.BTTPredefinedActionName: Run Apple Script (enter directly as text)

BTTTriggerConfig.BTTTouchBarAppleScriptString: if application "iTunes" is running then	tell application "iTunes"		if player state is stopped then			return ""		else			return "play"		end if	end tellend ifreturn ""

BTTTriggers.BTTPredefinedActionName: Run Apple Script (enter directly as text)
BTTTriggers.BTTInlineAppleScript: if application "iTunes" is running then	tell application "iTunes" to playpauseelse	do shell script "open -a iTunes"end if

BTTTriggerConfig.BTTTouchBarAppleScriptString: if application "iTunes" is running then	tell application "iTunes"		if player state is not stopped then return ""	end tellend ifif application "Safari" is running then	tell application "Safari"		repeat with t in tabs of windows			tell t				if URL starts with "https://music.yandex.ru" and name does not end with " ." then					return ""				end if			end tell		end repeat	end tellend ifreturn "play"

BTTTriggers.BTTPredefinedActionName: Open URL / Open URL With Selection

BTTTriggerConfig.BTTTouchBarAppleScriptString:
# This script requires two libs. Download them:# https://itunes.apple.com/ru/app/json-helper-for-applescript/id453114608?l=en&mt=12 if hours of (current date) is greater than 20 or hours of (current date) is less than 5 then	tell application "JSON Helper"		set weather to fetch JSON from "http://api.openweathermap.org/data/2.5/forecast?lat=55.018803&lon=82.933952&units=metric&appid=32c4256d09a4c52b38aecddba7a078f6&cnt=4"		set forecast to last item of |list| of weather		set temp to round (temp of main of forecast)		set wind to round (speed of wind of forecast)				return (temp as string) & "C
" & (wind as string) & "m/s"	end tellend ifreturn ""

BTTTriggers.BTTPredefinedActionName: Run Apple Script (enter directly as text)
BTTTriggers.BTTInlineAppleScript: if application "iTunes" is running then	tell application "iTunes"		playpause	end tellend if

BTTTriggerConfig.BTTTouchBarAppleScriptString: if application "iTunes" is running then	tell application "iTunes"		if player state is not stopped then			return (get artist of current track) & " - " & (get name of current track)		else			return ""		end if	end tellend ifreturn ""

tell application "Reminders"	set activeReminders to name of (reminders of list "" whose completed is false)	if activeReminders is not {} then		return first item of activeReminders	else		return ""	end ifend tell
